---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About – AngloEdge" description="Meet the team behind AngloEdge and our approach to UK capital markets intelligence.">
  <article class="max-w-prose mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <header class="mb-8">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-5xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">About AngloEdge</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          AngloEdge provides institutional-grade intelligence on UK capital markets for investors, founders, and policy participants who need to understand the mechanics of UK finance in real time.
        </p>
        <p>
          We distil regulatory shifts, macro dynamics, corporate transactions, and market structure into clear, actionable analysis. No noise. No consensus chasing. Just rigorous thinking about how UK markets actually work.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Our Approach</h2>
        <p>
          We believe the best analysis comes from deep domain expertise combined with cross-asset perspective. Our team has spent years in capital markets—trading floors, corporate development, investment committees, regulatory forums—and brings that practical experience to every briefing.
        </p>
        <p>
          We publish daily. We're not waiting for perfect information or consensus to calcify. We move at market speed, update our thinking constantly, and engage with the complexity of how markets actually function under uncertainty.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">The Team</h2>
        <p>
          AngloEdge is built by professionals with deep roots in UK capital markets. Our contributors include former traders, investment bankers, corporate strategists, and policy analysts who have worked across equities, credit, rates, and FX desks, as well as in corporate boardrooms and regulatory bodies.
        </p>
        <p>
          We work with specialist researchers and subject matter experts to ensure every briefing reflects current market conditions and the latest regulatory intelligence. Our network includes market participants, corporate executives, and policy insiders across the UK financial ecosystem.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Why AngloEdge?</h2>
        <p>
          The UK capital markets deserve better coverage. Most financial media chases headlines. Most research is backward-looking. Most commentary is consensus-driven.
        </p>
        <p>
          AngloEdge is different. We cover what matters—the structural shifts, the hidden incentives, the second-order consequences that move markets and shape outcomes. We write for people who need to understand, not for people who want their beliefs confirmed.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4">Subscribe & Connect</h2>
        <p>
          Daily briefings are free via RSS. For custom research, speaking engagements, or bespoke intelligence, <a href="/contact" class="text-navy hover:underline">get in touch</a>.
        </p>
        <p>
          Follow us on <a href="https://x.com/angloedgee" class="text-navy hover:underline">X (@angloedgee)</a> for real-time market commentary and briefing announcements.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  h2 {
    @apply font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-navy mt-8 mb-4;
  }

  p {
    @apply leading-tight text-gray-900 mb-4;
  }

  a {
    @apply text-navy hover:underline;
  }

  section {
    @apply mb-8;
  }
</style>
